T1  - Prevalence of dyslipidemia and associated factors in the older adults: ELSIA study.

T2  - Prevalencia de dislipidemia e fatores associados em idosos: estudo ELSIA.
A1  - Silva, Tamara Guimaraes
A1  - Galvao, Lucas Lima
