T1  - Hypertensive retinopathy and differential cardiovascular risk in black and white populations.

A1  - Garg, Ishaan
A1  - Said, Nada
A1  - Shaik, Abdullah
A1  - Seby, Robert
A1  - Alasmar, Rahmeh
A1  - Alhammouri, Hashim
