T1  - Cardiovascular health, genetic susceptibility, and the risk of ischemic stroke: a large prospective cohort study.

A1  - Huang, Yue-zhong
A1  - Ruan, Miao-hua
A1  - Zhang, Hao
A1  - Shen, Yi-fan
A1  - Zhou, Mi
A1  - Song, Hong-zi
A1  - Lu, Fan
