T1  - Exploring cardiovascular disease prevalence and contributing factors among adults in Southern Iran, a cross-sectional survey: rationale, design, and primary results.

A1  - Farshidi, Hossein
A1  - Nikparvar, Marzieh
A1  - Mohseni, Shokrollah
A1  - Eftekhar, Ebrahim
A1  - Dastsouz, Farideh
