T1  - Dietary inflammatory index and disability among older adults in Guangzhou: a cross-sectional analysis.

A1  - Liao, Jun-bin
A1  - Cai, Wen-feng
A1  - Lin, Dan-rong
A1  - Xiao, Yuan-yun
A1  - Liu, Yanxi
A1  - Wang, Ya-hui
A1  - Zhong, Yu-quan
A1  - Xiao, Fan
A1  - Fang, Heng
A1  - Yao, Yi-lu
A1  - Lin, Yun-feng
A1  - Su, Jie-wen
A1  - Sun, Si-yu
