T1  - The interaction between estimated glomerular filtration rate and dietary magnesium intake and its effect on stroke prevalence: a cross-sectional study spanning 2003-2018.

A1  - Liu, Chun-hua
A1  - Qiu, Lin-an
A1  - Zhang, Yuan-yuan
A1  - Chen, Li-ping
A1  - Wang, Hua-qiang
A1  - Lin, Hua-jian
