T1  - Bipolar disorder and the risk of cardiometabolic diseases, heart failure, and all-cause mortality: a population-based matched cohort study in South Korea.

A1  - Lee, You-Bin
A1  - Kim, Hyewon
A1  - Lee, Jungkuk
