T1  - Chronic hepatitis B virus infection and risk of stroke types: a prospective cohort study of 500 000 Chinese adults.

A1  - Hamilton, Elizabeth M.
A1  - Yang, Ling
A1  - Wright, Neil
A1  - Turnbull, Iain
A1  - Mentzer, Alexander J.
A1  - Matthews, Philippa C.
A1  - Chen, Yi-ping
A1  - Du, Huai-dong
A1  - Kartsonaki, Christiana
A1  - Pang, Yuan-jie
A1  - Pei, Pei
