T1  - Ultraprocessed foods and kidney disease progression, mortality, and cardiovascular disease risk in the CRIC study.

A1  - Sullivan, Valerie K.
A1  - Appel, Lawrence J.
A1  - Anderson, Cheryl A. M.
A1  - Kim, Hyunju
A1  - Unruh, Mark L.
A1  - Lash, James P.
A1  - Trego, Marsha
A1  - Sondheimer, James
A1  - Dobre, Mirela
A1  - Pradhan, Nishigandha
A1  - Rao, Panduranga S.
