T1  - Association between pneumonia hospitalisation and long-term risk of cardiovascular disease in Chinese adults: a prospective cohort study.

A1  - Hu, Yi-zhen
A1  - Sun, Zhi-jia
A1  - Yu, Can-qing
A1  - Guo, Yu
A1  - Pei, Pei
