T1  - Impact of cardiometabolic multimorbidity and ethnicity on cardiovascular/renal complications in patients with COVID-19.

A1  - Norris, Tom
A1  - Razieh, Cameron
A1  - Zaccardi, Francesco
A1  - Yates, Thomas
A1  - Islam, Nazrul
A1  - Gillies, Clare L.
