T1  - Association of serum choline levels and all-cause mortality risk in adults with hypertension: a nested case - control study.

A1  - Song, Meng-meng
A1  - Xu, Benjamin P.
A1  - Liang, Qiong-yue
A1  - Wei, Ya-ping
A1  - Song, Yun
A1  - Chen, Ping
