T1  - Lifecourse socioeconomic position and diabetes incidence in the reasons for geographic and racial differences in stroke (regards) study, 2003 to 2016.

A1  - Martin, Kimberly D.
A1  - Beckles, Gloria L.
A1  - Wu, Chengyi
