T1  - Associations of plasma metal concentrations with the risks of all-cause and cardiovascular disease mortality in Chinese adults.

A1  - Shi, Li-mei
A1  - Yuan, Yu
A1  - Xiao, Yang
A1  - Long, Pin-pin
A1  - Li, Wen-ding
A1  - Yu, Yan-qiu
A1  - Liu, Yi-yi
