T1  - Carotid artery stiffness in rural adult Chinese: a cross-sectional analysis of the community-based China stroke cohort study.

A1  - Wei, Yao
A1  - Wang, Ming
A1  - Gui, Yang
A1  - Piao, Xue-mei
